This is mostly a copy of the existing FastISel GEP code, but we have to duplicate it for <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/aarch64">AArch64</a>, because otherwise we would bail out even for simple cases.

This is because the standard fastEmit functions don&#39;t cover MUL at all and ADD is lowered very inefficientily.
